Well we used to deal in rabbits among ourselves we kids used to you see. Buy a rabbit for a tanner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid943631 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6899672\charrsid15295486 Can you tame ferrets so that they don't bite?
