\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid943631 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6899672\charrsid15295486 Did you used to go off on your own on these walks or did you go in a gang?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6576513 MA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6899672\charrsid15295486 
Oh generally two or three in a gang, you didn't as a rule go by yourself, unles
s you - you - only time you'd be by yourself when you reckoned you was going to meet somebody you know, see somebody in the morning say, meet thee down so and so, and then you'd walk to that spot and - by yourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid943631 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6899672\charrsid15295486 Did you do any sports at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6576513 MA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6899672\charrsid15295486 
Sport? Oh we used to play all sort - cricket and football among one another, all such does as that. Race. We played all they games. We hadn't got no - we hadn't got no field in - schooldays, you had to play - cricket in the - playground see and football 
on hard ground.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid943631 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6899672\charrsid15295486 Did you ever go to a theatre or concert when you were children?
